BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20140819T123000Z
DTEND:20140819T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260427T233835Z
UID:r56jd2l2bcme2dnp3u95upo038@google.com
CREATED:20140815T164225Z
DESCRIPTION:Staff and students alike will celebrate the start of the 2014-2
 015 school year at Dell Diamond on Tuesday\, August 19.\n\nThe event starts
  at 7:30 a.m. and will feature performances and fun prepared by Round Rock 
 ISD students and staff. Buses will arrive on campus at 6:30 a.m. to provide
  transportation. The RRISD team is encouraged to begin arriving at 7 a.m.\n
 \nAttendees are to dress casually within student dress code and all are enc
 ouraged to show school pride with their shirts. Employees are encouraged to
  bring one bottle of water.\n\nThe Round Rock Express will be providing eac
 h employee with a free ticket to that evening’s game as well as additional 
 discounted tickets for staff.\n\nLearn more by visiting RoundRockISD.org/Ki
 ckoff2014.
LAST-MODIFIED:20140815T164343Z
LOCATION:3400 E Palm Valley Blvd\, Round Rock\, TX 78665\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kickoff 2014 @ Dell Diamond
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
