UID:5ovpgm22mh74feiqadmi2atuso@google.com
CREATED:20140109T175823Z
DESCRIPTION:Conversations/Pláticas is a resource available to Spanish-speak
 ing parents that provides valuable district\, campus\, and community inform
 ation in their native language.  Conversations/Pláticas began at Round Rock
  High School in October 2008.  This resource is available to parents of stu
 dents in Round Rock ISD in all grade levels.  Topics discussed include\, bu
 t are not limited to\, attendance\, school services\, college preparation\,
  scholarships\, school safety\, etc.\n\nLight refreshments\, helpful inform
 ation\, support\, and fellowship are provided.
LAST-MODIFIED:20140109T175823Z
LOCATION:Hernandez Middle School\, 1901 Sunrise Road\, Round Rock\, TX\, Un
 ited States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Conversations/Pláticas
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
