CREATED:20120716T140454Z
DESCRIPTION:Round Rock ISD is pleased to introduce the district’s new Deput
 y Superintendent of Instruction and Administration\, Dr. Martha Salazar-Zam
 ora\, as well as the district’s new Assistant Superintendent of Elementary 
 Education\, Carla Amacher and Assistant Superintendent of Secondary Educati
 on\, Rebecca Donald.\n\nThe district will hold a welcome reception on Monda
 y\, July 16 from 4 p.m. to 6 p.m. in the Round Rock High School new cafeter
 ia\, 300 Lake Creek Drive in Round Rock. Superintendent Dr. Jesus H. Chavez
  will address attendees at 5 p.m.\n\nPlease RSVP to the Community Relations
  Department at 512-464-5113 or community_relations@roundrockisd.org
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T012037Z
LOCATION:Round Rock HS new Cafeteria
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Reception for new Deputy Superintendent
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
