BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20160711
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20160712
DTSTAMP:20260427T233835Z
UID:4ousk847r43ou36bpk9g6c14co@google.com
CREATED:20160609T190305Z
DESCRIPTION:The following documents are needed for new student registration
 :\nPROOF OF RESIDENCE: Guardian/Parent Name on current lease\, contract of 
 sale\, utility bill\nWITHDRAWAL FORM/TRANSCRIPT: If registering during scho
 ol year OR\nFINAL REPORT CARD/TRANSCRIPT: If registering during summer\nIMM
 UNIZATION RECORDS: Must be in hand\, see requirements below\nBIRTH CERTIFIC
 ATE: 30 day grace period\nSOCIAL SECURITY CARD\nMUST LIVE WITH PARENTS OR L
 EGAL GUARDIANS\nIMMUNIZATION REQUIREMENTS\nTexas law requires all students 
 to be immunized for certain diseases. According to school policy\, children
  may be exempted from the requirements if parent/guardian furnishes certifi
 cation from a physician stating one or more of the immunizations would enda
 nger the child’s life or a certificate from the Texas Department of Health.
 \n\nImmunizations will be required for the following diseases:\nDT/DTP/DTAP
 3 Doses\nincluding 1 dose on or after 4th birthday\nTDAP Booster1 Dose 10 y
 ears after last does of DTP/DTAP/DT\nPOLIO4 Doses unless 3rd dose is on or 
 after 4th birthday\nMMR2 Doses separated by 30 days\, on or after 1st birth
 day\nVARICELLA(No disease)2 Doses on or after 13yr\n1 Dose on or after 1st 
 birthday\nHEPATITIS-B3 Doses\nMENINGOCOCCAL1 Dose
LAST-MODIFIED:20160609T190305Z
LOCATION:https://roundrockisd.org/enroll/
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:New Student Enrollment Opens
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
