BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20120816T230000Z
DTEND:20120817T020000Z
DTSTAMP:20260427T233835Z
UID:eu6ju9dl14r625nk1h5sn85cps@google.com
CREATED:20120809T161007Z
DESCRIPTION:It’s not too late for 2012 graduates to apply for college for t
 he upcoming Fall semester. The Round Rock ISD Guidance and Counseling Depar
 tment\, in conjunction with Austin Community College (ACC) and Texas State 
 Technical College (TSTC) is hosting a College Enrollment Event on Thursday\
 , August 16 at 6 p.m. in the Round Rock High School new cafeteria\, 300 N. 
 Lake Creek in Round Rock. \n\nRecent graduates will have the opportunity to
  register for certificate or 2-year degree programs at ACC or TSTC. Both in
 stitutions offer local classes and some certificate programs which can be c
 ompleted in as little as six months. At the event\, participants will be ab
 le to apply to the college\, apply for financial assistance and register fo
 r classes with college counselors. \n\nFood\, prizes and babysitting will b
 e available at the event for 2012 graduates and their parents.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T011942Z
LOCATION:Round Rock High School new cafeteria\, 300 Lake Creek Drive\, Roun
 d Rock\, TX 78681
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:College Enrollment Event
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
