 Spanish-speaking parents entitled "Pláticas" or "Conversations." \n\nThese 
 gatherings are for parents of students of all ages in Round Rock ISD\, and 
 provide opportunities for parents to discuss issues such as attendance\, co
 llege preparation\, school services and more. For more information\, contac
 t Maria Rosas Garcia at 428-7984 or maria_rosasgarcia@roundrockisd.org
