UID:01s1ccikcp4qqrpmgd8ij9b9e2@google.com
CREATED:20210427T140613Z
DESCRIPTION:Round Rock ISD’s Counseling Services will host the 2021 Virtual
  College & Career Action Expo for graduating seniors on Monday\, May 3 from
  2 to 4 p.m.\n\nThe Expo will assist students who have not yet settled on p
 ost graduation plans. Opportunities will be available for students to speak
  with representatives from colleges still accepting applications for the fa
 ll\, businesses with job openings\, and military recruiters.\n\nAssistance 
 will also be available for students who have not yet completed their FAFSA®
  or TASFA applications.\n\nAlthough this event will be held virtually\, sen
 iors are encouraged to dress in business attire. It’s also encouraged to ch
 ange your Zoom name to your full first and last name.
LAST-MODIFIED:20210427T140613Z
LOCATION:https://zoom.us/j/92215012368?pwd=T3FEcEFsVWtBS05lckY2SEZGb3ltZz09
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Career Action Expo
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
