 nnual Powderpuff Football Tournament May 21 at Kelly Reeves Athletic Comple
 x.\n\nThe event will begin at 10 a.m. and feature games from RRISD high sch
 ools. Tickets will be $2 for children and students and $3 for adults. T-shi
 rts and concessions will be sold and all donations and proceeds will go to 
 The Backpack Coalition.
