UID:12jnmlfoid4fnbch84l50gi18i@google.com
CREATED:20210226T172739Z
DESCRIPTION:The Round Rock Independent School District is hosting public he
 arings for community feedback on potential adjustments to school boundaries
 . Community members can watch the hearings on the <a href="https://roundroc
 kisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting websi
 te</a>. Individuals that wish to provide feedback may do so by filling out 
 the&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScrjYMMwR2OI
 iG1s18hhFT-H76lcr77PrLhbVfiDsPQb37PlA/viewform?gxids=7628">Boundary Hearing
  Speaker Registration Form</a></b>&nbsp\;by noon on the day of each meeting
 . Speakers may sign up for one or both meetings and will be provided with a
  Zoom link prior to the hearing. Speakers will have two minutes to provide 
 feedback.<br><br>For those unable to watch live\, hearings will be availabl
 e to view after the meeting on the <a href="https://roundrockisd.org/about-
 rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting website.</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210226T172754Z
LOCATION: https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meet
 ings/ (map)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Boundary Hearing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
