DESCRIPTION:Notice is hereby given that the Safety and Security Committee o
 f the Round RockIndependent School District will hold a Regular Meeting on 
 Tuesday\, August 17\,2021 at 6:00 pm in the Board Room of the Lillie Delgad
 o Administration Building\,1311 Round Rock Avenue\, Round Rock\, Texas 7868
 1 to consider the subjectsindicated\, and the locations listed in the Agend
 a\, a copy which is attached heretoand incorporated hereto by reference.<br
 ><br><p>1. Call Meeting to Order&nbsp\;</p><p>2. Public Comment&nbsp\;</p><
 p>The Committee will afford members of the public an opportunity to speak o
 n items listed on the agenda. Individuals wishing to address the Committee 
 must sign up beginning one (1) hour prior to the meeting's posted start tim
 e and end by the posted start time.&nbsp\;</p><p>3. EXECUTIVE SESSION may b
 e called for the purposes permitted by the Texas Open Meetings Act\, Texas 
 Government Code Section 551.076&nbsp\;</p><p>4. Overview of Safety and Secu
 rity Assessment\, Campus Audit Round Rock High School&nbsp\;</p><p>Presente
 r: Jim Williby\, Assistant Chief of Police&nbsp\;</p><p>5. Closing Remarks&
 nbsp\;</p><p>6. Meeting Adjourned&nbsp\;</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210812T205039Z
LOCATION:1311 Round Rock Ave\, Round Rock\, TX 78681\, USA - Board Room
