DESCRIPTION:￼￼￼￼Healthy Lifestyles PTA of\nRound Rock ISD\nPresents\n\n\n￼￼
 ￼￼￼\n￼Join us for\nFree Family Fun!\n\nSaturday from noon–3:00pm MARCH 5TH 
 Purple Sage Elementary\n11801 Tanglebriar Trail Austin\, TX 78750\n\n￼￼￼Act
 ivities include\nRock climbing wall\, mechanical bull\, dancing\, board bre
 aking\ncontest\, yoga\, “Amazing RaceTM” obstacle course\, facials\, massag
 es\, reflexology\, sports drills\, cross fit\, nutrition\, cooking demonstr
 ations\, healthy food samples\, medical screenings and SO much more!\n\nADV
 ENTURE Run begins at 12:30 p.m. on the El Salido Trail behind the school\, 
 prizes for top finishers. ADULTS you are invited too.\n\nBRING YOUR BIKE fo
 r a free safety check\nCONTACT: Leslie Cullers\, 512- 797-9961\n\n“Approval
  of distribution of these materials is in no way an endorsement of such ser
 vices\, activities\, and/or products by the Round Rock Independent School D
 istrict.”\n￼￼
