CREATED:20210202T143809Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Community members can watch the hearings on the&nbsp\;<a hre
 f="https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meetings/">
 Board Meeting website</a>. Individuals that wish to provide feedback may do
  so by filling out the&nbsp\;<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FA
 IpQLSfJ2gwzIjsgY2LTAccsv1xEyARKmrZkAXWpw2WbV_JGacxa_Q/closedform">Boundary 
 Hearing Speaker Registration Form&nbsp\;</a>by noon on the day of each meet
 ing. Speakers may sign up for one or both meetings and will be provided wit
 h a Zoom link prior to the hearing. Speakers will have two minutes to provi
 de feedback.</p><p>For those unable to watch live\, hearings will be availa
 ble to view after the meeting on the&nbsp\;<a href="https://roundrockisd.or
 g/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting website.</a>
 &nbsp\;<a href="mailto:boundaries_rrisd@roundrockisd.org">Submit your bound
 ary questions</a>.</p>
