CREATED:20140109T213017Z
DESCRIPTION:This event is sponsored by the RRISD student chapter of the Fut
 ure Music Educators Association\, consisting of high school students who ar
 e interested in a career as music educators. \n\nThis annual performance is
  designed to provide an opportunity for students and the community to hear 
 our outstanding RRISD band\, choir\, and orchestra directors\, as well as e
 lementary music teachers\, perform in public. The music will include solo p
 erformances as well as an eclectic variety of vocal and instrumental ensemb
 les.\n\nThe event is free to the public\, although donations will be accept
 ed for a special fund that will help provide partial scholarships for priva
 te music lessons for students that need financial aid.
LAST-MODIFIED:20140121T230112Z
LOCATION:Raymond E. Hartfield Performing Arts Center\, 5800 McNeil Road\, A
 ustin\, 78729
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Fifth Annual Faculty Recital
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
