BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20130302T140000Z
DTEND:20130302T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260427T233835Z
UID:voskebo79pf5aonanhpim8epbs@google.com
CREATED:20130110T205730Z
DESCRIPTION:The RRISD Project Graduation organization is hosting the 9th An
 nual Round Rock ISD Project Graduation 5K Run/Walk and Kids 1K Fun Run/Walk
  on Saturday\, March 2 at the Dell Diamond. The event\, sponsored by Seton 
 Medical Center Williamson\, is a district-wide fundraiser to benefit all Ro
 und Rock ISD high schools and their graduating seniors in 2013. The day wil
 l be full of special activities in and around Dell Diamond\, so plan on sta
 ying after the race for family fun events. \n\nProject Graduation is an all
 -night lock-in party held the night of graduation for seniors to have a saf
 e place to celebrate and be with friends. Race registration is available on
 line\, and includes a race packet and t-shirt (guaranteed t-shirt for entri
 es received by Feb. 18\, after that while supplies last). Entry fee increas
 es from $20 to $25 on Feb. 25. Online registration ends Wednesday\, Feb. 27
 . Entry fee increases to $30 on race day\, March 2. All RRISD students and 
 employees receive a $5 discount. \n\nMore information and to register onlin
 e\nhttp://site.runtex.com/index.php/2013/01/9th-annual-round-rock-isd-proje
 ct-graduation-5k/
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T011855Z
LOCATION:Dell Diamond
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Project Grad 5K
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
