BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20120515T220000Z
DTEND:20120515T233000Z
DTSTAMP:20260427T233835Z
UID:kh7n8eaphjv8s9qai7pqfcakao@google.com
CREATED:20120509T170851Z
DESCRIPTION:You're invited to see the fantastic creations of some of Round 
 Rock ISD's most innovative students. \n\nWatch our first Sumo bot challenge
 ! Be there to cheer for your favorite robot. \n\nIn a robot Sumo match\, tw
 o robots start inside a ring marked with a border of a contrasting color an
 d try to be the first one to push the other robot outside the ring (without
  accidentally driving outside the ring themselves). \n\nAlso\, students wil
 l present robots created throughout the school year. This showcase will dem
 onstrate the problem solving and programming skills students learned using 
 Lego NXT and other applications. \n\nSee their exciting demonstrations in a
 ction! \n\nSee what the robotics teams from elementary\, middle\, and high 
 schools have created both in the classroom and in competition. \n\nHelp us 
 applaud the Round Rock ISD teams who participated in competitions this past
  year.\n\nMore information on the Robotics Showcase\nhttp://schools.roundro
 ckisd.org/caldwellheight/robotics/robotics/index.html
LAST-MODIFIED:20120509T171030Z
LOCATION:McNeil HS Cafeteria -  5720 McNeil Drive Austin\, Texas 78729  
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:3rd Annual Robotics Showcase
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
