UID:703si88vqs1rj2tmf8rot4rd53@google.com
CREATED:20210202T143951Z
DESCRIPTION:The Round Rock Independent School District is hosting public he
 arings for community feedback on potential adjustments to <a href="https://
 news.roundrockisd.org/">school boundaries</a>. Community members can watch 
 the hearings on the <a href="https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-
 trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting website</a>. Individuals that wish 
 to provide feedback may do so by filling out the Boundary Hearing Speaker R
 egistration Form by noon on the day of each meeting. Speakers may sign up f
 or one or both meetings and will be provided with a Zoom link prior to the 
 hearing. Speakers will have two minutes to provide feedback.<br><br><b><a h
 ref="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfJ2gwzIjsgY2LTAccsv1xEyARKmr
 ZkAXWpw2WbV_JGacxa_Q/viewform?gxids=7628" id="ow2215" __is_owner="true">Bou
 ndary Hearing Speaker Registration Form</a></b><br><br>For those unable to 
 watch live\, hearings will be available to view after the meeting on the <a
  href="https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meeting
 s/">Board Meeting website.</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210210T163955Z
LOCATION:https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meeti
 ngs/
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Boundary Hearing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
