DESCRIPTION:<br>The Round Rock Independent School District is hosting publi
 c hearings for community feedback on potential adjustments to school bounda
 ries. Community members can watch the hearings on the <a href="https://roun
 drockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting w
 ebsite</a>. Individuals that wish to provide feedback may do so by filling 
 out the&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScrjYMMw
 R2OIiG1s18hhFT-H76lcr77PrLhbVfiDsPQb37PlA/viewform?gxids=7628" id="ow784" _
 _is_owner="true">Boundary Hearing Speaker Registration Form</a></b>&nbsp\;b
 y noon on the day of each meeting. Speakers may sign up for one or both mee
 tings and will be provided with a Zoom link prior to the hearing. Speakers 
 will have two minutes to provide feedback.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><
 br>For those unable to watch live\, hearings will be available to view afte
 r the meeting on the <a href="https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of
 -trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting website.</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210226T172548Z
LOCATION: https://roundrockisd.org/about-rrisd/board-of-trustees/board-meet
 ings/ (map)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Boundary Hearing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
