DESCRIPTION:A Community Meeting with Superintendent Dr. Jesús H. Chávez wil
 l be held Tuesday\, August 21 from 5:30 p.m. to 7:00 p.m. at Mimi’s Cafe\, 
 4151 N. IH-35 in the Round Rock Premium Outlets center. \n\n The Meeting is
  a chance for community members to meet Dr. Chávez and discuss current and 
 future goals for RRISD\, previous Bond Programs\, parent involvement opport
 unities\, and the state of the district as well as address any questions. L
 ight refreshments will be provided by the Round Rock ISD Partners in Educat
 ion Foundation. Please RSVP by noon on Monday\, August 20.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T011903Z
LOCATION:Mimi's Cafe\, 4151 N. IH-35\, Round Rock\, TX 78665
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Community Meeting with the Superintendent
TRANSP:OPAQUE
