DESCRIPTION:Conversations/Pláticas is a resource available to Spanish-speak
 ing parents that provides valuable district\, campus\, and community inform
 ation in their native language.  Conversations/Pláticas began at Round Rock
  High School in October 2008. This resource is available to parents of stud
 ents in Round Rock ISD in all grade levels. Topics discussed include\, but 
 are not limited to\, attendance\, school services\, college preparation\, s
 cholarships\, school safety\, etc.\n\nMeetings are held in a variety of Rou
 nd Rock locations throughout the school year. Light refreshments\, helpful 
 information\, support\, and fellowship are provided.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T011944Z
LOCATION:Bluebonnet ES Library\, 101 Chisholm Valley Drive\, Round Rock
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Conversations/Pláticas
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
