UID:6mvu0aiakre3nefif30f80uojl@google.com
CREATED:20210209T155745Z
DESCRIPTION:The Round Rock Independent School District is hosting public he
 arings for community feedback on potential adjustments to&nbsp\;<a href="ht
 tps://news.roundrockisd.org/">school boundaries</a>. Community members can 
 watch the hearings on the&nbsp\;<a href="https://roundrockisd.org/about-rri
 sd/board-of-trustees/board-meetings/">Board Meeting website</a>. Individual
 s that wish to provide feedback may do so by filling out the Boundary Heari
 ng Speaker Registration Form by noon on the day of each meeting. Speakers m
 ay sign up for one or both meetings and will be provided with a Zoom link p
 rior to the hearing. Speakers will have two minutes to provide feedback.<br
