DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">We are grateful that we are able to provide health
  and wellness education\, resources and opportunities for all our Round Roc
 k ISD community! That’s why we are providing two free health and wellness f
 airs for students and families before school ends.</p><p dir="ltr">You’re i
 nvited to meet with health and wellness specialists and community vendors b
 etween the six breakout sessions and free pizza (while it lasts).</p><p dir
 ="ltr"><b>Topics covered:<br></b>- Student support through academic transit
 ion<br>- Stress management and mental health awareness<br>- CPR &amp\; Stop
  The Bleed demos<br>- Internet safety<br>- Physical fitness activities</p>
