 omplete new in-district &amp\; out-of-district student enrollment and get<b
 r>help with annual forms.<br>• Sign up for fun and affordable camps.<br>• F
 amilies whose students are invited to participate in our Launch\, Propel an
 d<br>high school summer learning can get their questions answered and<br>in
 -person help enrolling.<br>• Learn about our virtual learning program.<br>•
  Get guidance directly from our subject matter experts.<br>• Enjoy refreshm
 ents while your student enjoys fun activities.<br><br><b>Have a new student
  you'd like to enroll?<br></b><br><u>Make sure to bring these documents\, a
 nd we'll get you enrolled!<br></u>• Student’s certified birth certificate\,
 <br>• Immunization records\,<br>• Proof of residence within the school dist
 rict<br>• Boundaries\, or bring your district transfer approval.<br>• The l
 ast report card or withdrawal form from the prior school district (if avail
 able)\, <br>• The student’s Social Security Card (if available).
