DESCRIPTION:Earn your high school diploma and a <b>free</b> Associate's deg
 ree from ACC.<br>Don't miss this opportunity. Declare your interest early.<
 br><br>Eighth-grade students\, with their families\, are encouraged to atte
 nd this in-person event.<br><br><b>ECHS\, located at the ACC Round Rock cam
 pus\, 4400 College Park Dr.<br></b>- Students in grades 9 through 12 enjoy 
 a small school experience.<br>- Earn a diploma and up to 60 free transferab
 le college credit hours.<br>- Accountability Rating: A - Exemplary Performa
 nce\, with high student satisfaction.<br>- Strong student support services.
 <br>- Student-driven clubs\, activities\, and leadership opportunities.<br>
 - UIL academics. UIL sports &amp\; fine arts are unavailable.<br>- Tuition\
 , textbooks &amp\; in-district transportation included.<br>- Enroll and lea
 rn more at <a href="http://rrisdschools.org/ECHS" target="_blank">rrisdscho
 ols.org/ECHS</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260106T165554Z
