DESCRIPTION:Earn your high school diploma and a <b>free</b> Associate&#39\;
 s degree from ACC.<br>Don&#39\;t miss this opportunity. Declare your intere
 st early.<br><br>Round Rock ISD Early College High School &amp\; P-TECH Nur
 sing Early College High School are enrolling for the 2026-27 school year!<b
 r><br>Eighth-grade students\, with their families\, are encouraged to atten
 d this in-person event.<br><br><b>ECHS\, located at the ACC Round Rock camp
 us\, 4400 College Park Dr.<br></b>- Students in grades 9 through 12 enjoy a
  small school experience.<br>- Earn a diploma and up to 60 free transferabl
 e college credit hours.<br>- Accountability Rating: A - Exemplary Performan
 ce\, with high student satisfaction.<br>- Strong student support services.<
 br>- Student-driven clubs\, activities\, and leadership opportunities.<br>-
  UIL academics. UIL sports &amp\; fine arts are unavailable.<br>- Tuition\,
  textbooks &amp\; in-district transportation included.<br>- Enroll and lear
 n more at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://rrisdschools.org/ECH
 S&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1757887463754780&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3
 oXJIqqlH6jv-425VOUa9a" target="_blank">rrisdschools.org/ECHS</a><br><br><b>
 P-TECH\, located at Cedar Ridge High School\, 2801 Gattis School Rd.<br></b
 >- Students in grades 9 through 12 combine high school\, college\, and work
 place learning on a pathway to become a licensed vocational nurse.<br>- Stu
 dents can earn a high school diploma\, industry-based certifications\, and 
 college credits towards an Associate of Applied Science degree at no cost.<
 br>- Partnerships with ACC and St. David&#39\;s Healthcare.<br>-The applica
 tion deadline is Friday\, January 30\, 2026.<br>-Tuition\, textbooks &amp\;
  in-district transportation included.<br>- Enroll and learn more at <a href
 ="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://rrisdschools.org/P-TECH&amp\;sa=D&am
