CREATED:20131007T141937Z
DESCRIPTION:CANCELLED: Conversations/Pláticas is a resource available to Sp
 anish-speaking parents that provides valuable district\, campus\, and commu
 nity information in their native language.  Conversations/Pláticas began at
  Round Rock High School in October 2008. This resource is available to pare
 nts of students in Round Rock ISD in all grade levels. Topics discussed inc
 lude\, but are not limited to\, attendance\, school services\, college prep
 aration\, scholarships\, school safety\, etc.\n\nMeetings are held in a var
 iety of Round Rock locations throughout the school year. Light refreshments
 \, helpful information\, support\, and fellowship are provided.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T012510Z
LOCATION:CANCELLED: RRISD's Family Resource Center\, 1311 Round Rock Ave.\,
  Round Rock
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CANCELLED: Conversations/Pláticas
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
