DESCRIPTION:Old Town Elementary will celebrate its 25th anniversary as a sc
 hool Wednesday\, November 13 from 6 to 7:30 p.m. in the campus cafeteria. O
 ld Town is located at 2200 Chaparral Drive\, Round Rock.\n\nFormer and curr
 ent students and staff and other members of the community are invited to at
 tend the festivities. Round Rock Mayor Alan McGraw will speak at the event 
 and members of the Round Rock ISD Board of Trustees will be in attendance.\
 n\nThe program will also feature a musical performance by Old Town fourth-g
 rade students and essay readings. Refreshments will be served after the pro
 gram.\n\nOld Town Elementary opened its doors for the 1988-89 school year.
