DESCRIPTION:Conversations/Pláticas is a resource available to Spanish-speak
 ing parents that provides valuable district\, campus\, and community inform
 ation in their native language.  \n\nConversations/Pláticas began at Round 
 Rock High School in October 2008. This resource is available to parents of 
 students in Round Rock ISD in all grade levels. Topics discussed include\, 
 but are not limited to\, attendance\, school services\, college preparation
 \, scholarships\, school safety\, etc.\n\nMeetings are held in a variety of
  Round Rock locations throughout the school year. Light refreshments\, help
 ful information\, support\, and fellowship are provided.
