DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr"><b>Ten Skills GT Students Need for the Future</b><
 /p><p dir="ltr">Ferris Bueller once said\, "Life moves pretty fast. If you 
 don't stop and look around once in a while\, you could miss it." The moveme
 nt we see now is in the workforce\, and it is changing at warp speed. The s
 kills needed today include critical and creative thinking\, relational capa
 city\, the ability to manage change\, and more. This session will explore a
  set of critical skills that reflect lifelong learning for future success. 
 </p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://meet.google.com/bbw-nxug-oiq?authuser=0&a
 mp\;hs=122"><u>Join with Google Meet</u></a><br>meet.google.com/bbw-nxug-oi
 q</p><p dir="ltr">Join by phone<br>(US) +1 385-404-0742‬ PIN: ‪924 049 576‬
 #</p>
