 ree from ACC.<br>Don't miss this opportunity. Declare your interest early.<
 br><br>Round Rock ISD Early College High School &amp\; P-TECH Nursing Early
  College High School are enrolling for the 2026-27 school year!<br><br>Eigh
 th-grade students\, with their families\, are encouraged to attend this in-
 person event.<br><br><b>ECHS\, located at the ACC Round Rock campus\, 4400 
 College Park Dr.<br></b>- Students in grades 9 through 12 enjoy a small sch
 ool experience.<br>- Earn a diploma and up to 60 free transferable college 
 credit hours.<br>- Accountability Rating: A - Exemplary Performance\, with 
 high student satisfaction.<br>- Strong student support services.<br>- Stude
 nt-driven clubs\, activities\, and leadership opportunities.<br>- UIL acade
 mics. UIL sports &amp\; fine arts are unavailable.<br>- Tuition\, textbooks
  &amp\; in-district transportation included.<br>- Enroll and learn more at 
 <a target="_blank" href="http://rrisdschools.org/ECHS">rrisdschools.org/ECH
 S</a><br><br><b>P-TECH\, located at Cedar Ridge High School\, 2801 Gattis S
 chool Rd.<br></b>- Students in grades 9 through 12 combine high school\, co
 llege\, and workplace learning on a pathway to become a licensed vocational
  nurse.<br>- Students can earn a high school diploma\, industry-based certi
 fications\, and college credits towards an Associate of Applied Science deg
 ree at no cost.<br>- Partnerships with ACC and St. David's Healthcare.<br>-
 The application deadline is Friday\, January 30\, 2026.<br>-Tuition\, textb
 ooks &amp\; in-district transportation included.<br>- Enroll and learn more
  at <a target="_blank" href="https://rrisdschools.org/P-TECH">https://rrisd
 schools.org/P-TECH</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250909T220218Z
LOCATION:Pearson Ranch Middle School\, 8901 Pearson Ranch Rd\, Austin\, TX 
 78717\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Early College High School & PTECH Nursing Info Session
TRANSP:OPAQUE
