CREATED:20260408T172930Z
DESCRIPTION:Join our Enrichment Department as they host the Middle School R
 obotics Competition and the Elementary Robotics Showcase! <br><br><b>The Mi
 ddle School Robotics Competition</b> is for our middle school robotics team
 s who are competing in the VEX Robotics competitions. <br><br><b>Middle Sch
 ool Robotics Competition:</b><br>Check-in &amp\; Inspections - 8-9 a.m. <br
 >Qualifying Rounds - 9-11:30 a.m. <br>Lunch Break - 11:30-12:15 p.m.<br>Qua
 lifying/Alliance Selections - 12:15-1:30 p.m. <br>Single Elimination Tourna
 ment - 1:30-2:30 p.m. <br>Awards - 2:30-3 p.m. <br><br><b>The Elementary Ro
 botics Showcase</b> is for Elementary robotics clubs and their families\; t
 hey are invited to join their vertical learning communities for a time to s
 how what they have learned in robotics this school year. <br><br>During thi
 s time\, students will have the opportunity to showcase their robot builds 
 and to run the challenges they have been working on during their weekly clu
 b time. It will be a great opportunity for our students to see how their pe
 ers from another campus solved a task. <i>*Students may not be dropped off 
 without their guardians.</i><br><br><b>Elementary Robotics Showcase:</b><br
 >Westwood Learning Community - 8-9 a.m.<br>Stony Point Learning Community -
  9:30-10:30 a.m.<br>Cedar Ridge Learning Community - 11 a.m.-12 p.m.<br>Rou
 nd Rock Learning Community - 1-2 p.m.<br>McNeil Learning Community - 2:30-3
 :30 p.m.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260408T172936Z
LOCATION:Round Rock High School\, 201 Deep Wood Dr\, Round Rock\, TX 78681\
 , USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Robotics Extravaganza
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
