CREATED:20130502T132832Z
DESCRIPTION:State and Federal Programs is hosting a meeting for parents of 
 Title I students on Tuesday\, May 21 from 4:30 - 6:00 p.m. The meeting will
  be held in the Old Hopewell building\, 1311 Round Rock Ave.\, Round Rock.\
 n\nThe purpose of this meeting is to discuss and review the district’s Pare
 nt Involvement Policy\, Parent Programs\, Practical Parent Education curric
 ulum\, Celebration of Families planning and services to Title I students.\n
 \nYour input and guidance is sought to help our district continue to provid
 e the highest level of service\, effective programming and interventions fo
 r your child’s academic success.\n\nPlease consider joining our discussion.
  The meeting will be informal and light snacks will be provided. Child care
  will also be available during the meeting. If you are unable to stay for t
 he entire meeting\, we welcome and appreciate any time you can spend with u
 s.\n\nAll district parents of Title I students are welcome! 
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T012220Z
LOCATION:RRISD Old Hopewell Building
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Title I District Parent Meeting
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
