DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr"><b>AP Capstone - A Perfect Pairing for Gifted High
  School Students</b></p><p dir="ltr">The College Board AP Capstone Diploma 
 is based on two year-long courses: AP Seminar and AP Research\, along with 
 at least four other AP courses of the student’s choice. Rather than teachin
 g specific subject knowledge\, AP Seminar and AP Research use an interdisci
 plinary approach to develop the critical thinking\, research\, collaboratio
 n\, time management\, and presentation skills necessary for success in coll
 ege. Learn more about this unique opportunity\, a perfect match for gifted 
 learners.</p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://meet.google.com/iin-bsuz-ybk?aut
 huser=0&amp\;hs=122">Join with Google Meet</a><br>meet.google.com/iin-bsuz-
 ybk</p><p dir="ltr">Join by phone<br>(US) +1 754-702-8274‬ PIN: ‪710 235 95
 0‬#</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T193847Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Talented and Gifted Lunch and Learn 3
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
