 ng at 8:00 AM. In accordance with the waiver to certain provisions of the T
 exas Open Meetings Act issued by Governor Greg Abbott on March 16\, 2020\, 
 trustees will participate remotely by teleconference or videoconference. Pl
 ease note that there is no physical location for the public to attend this 
