DESCRIPTION:The Round Rock ISD surplus store sale is Wednesday\, Oct. 30 fr
 om 10 a.m. to 3 p.m. at 16255 Great Oaks Drive\, Suite 500. An array of Del
 l laptops and desktops will be available for purchase along with items such
  as monitors\, office furniture\, laptop bags\, printers and other miscella
 neous electronics. The store accepts cash\, checks (with local\, valid ID) 
 and all major credit cards. All purchases are considered “as is.” No refund
 s will be made. Items must also be picked up at the time of purchase.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T012638Z
LOCATION:16255 Great Oaks Drive\, Suite 500\, Round Rock\, TX
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Surplus Store Sale
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
