DESCRIPTION:Round Rock ISD is once again hosting its monthly workshops for 
 Spanish-speaking parents entitled "Pláticas" or "Conversations." The first 
 such gathering will be held Sept. 4 in the Voigt Elementary Cafeteria\, 120
 1 Cushing Drive\, from 6-8 p.m. These gatherings are for parents of student
 s of all ages in Round Rock ISD\, and provide opportunities for parents to 
 discuss issues such as attendance\, college preparation\, school services a
 nd more. For more information\, contact Maria Rosas Garcia at 428-7984 or m
 aria_rosasgarcia@roundrockisd.org
LAST-MODIFIED:20230307T012218Z
LOCATION:Voigt Elementary Cafeteria\, 1201 Cushing Dr.\, Round Rock\, TX
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Platicas/Conversations
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
